The paper deals with approximation algorithms for independent set in geometric graphs, which is a topic in computational geometry (cs.CG) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of approximation algorithms also suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-category of discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The analysis of worst-case update times and approximation ratios involves complexity theory (cs.CC) and numerical analysis (cs.NA).
